The '''Apricot''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] grown by planting an [[Apricot Sapling]], waiting 28 days for it to grow into an [[Apricot Tree]], and harvesting the tree during the [[Spring]].

An Apricot may be purchased at the [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|50}} or found in [[The Cave|The Farm Cave]], if the fruit bat option is chosen.

