==Tailoring==
Apricot can be used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[Tailoring#Pants|Relaxed Fit Pants]].  [[File:Relaxed Fit Pants.png|36px]] It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as an orange dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].

==Quests==
[[Emily]] requests an apricot by mail on the 6th of [[Spring]] (year 2) in the [[Quests#Fresh Fruit|"Fresh Fruit" Quest]].  The reward is {{Price|600}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.

==History==
{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}

